CCTermConnEv
public abstract class CCCallEv
extends FreeCallEvent
implements javax.telephony.callcontrol.events.CallCtlCallEv

This is the CallControl Call (and therefore TerminalConnection) event superclass.

When a Call or TerminalConnection event is displatched, its CallControl twin should also be dispatched if the Observer implements CallControlCallObserver. Creation date: (2000-08-03 11:19:22)
